00:02:02.041 --> 00:02:04.125
But this monk doesn't look like a bad person.

00:02:04.166 --> 00:02:06.000
You may know a person's face but not their heart.

00:02:06.500 --> 00:02:07.583
Who can say?

00:02:08.666 --> 00:02:09.333
Lin Xiaoran

00:02:09.375 --> 00:02:10.041
Hmm.

00:02:10.375 --> 00:02:11.875
It's been almost three days.

00:02:12.333 --> 00:02:13.666
It seems I overestimated you.

00:02:15.875 --> 00:02:16.958
Your Excellency

00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:19.583
County magistrate Sun

00:02:19.875 --> 00:02:22.083
Liu Gui was obsessed with dark rituals and abused his adopted daughters.

00:02:22.208 --> 00:02:24.458
After his crimes were exposed, he committed suicide out of guilt.

00:02:24.625 --> 00:02:25.583
You may close the case.

00:02:25.666 --> 00:02:27.125
What? This...

00:02:27.291 --> 00:02:29.833
Are we really not letting the coroner examine the bodies again?

00:02:30.250 --> 00:02:31.250
County magistrate Sun

00:02:31.625 --> 00:02:33.583
I saw through Liu Gui long ago.

00:02:33.666 --> 00:02:35.583
He was frail and short of breath in life.

00:02:35.833 --> 00:02:37.125
He suffered from yin deficiency and yang depletion.

00:02:37.208 --> 00:02:39.750
He built this corpse bed to absorb yin to supplement yang.

00:02:39.791 --> 00:02:40.916
To prolong life and enhance desire.

00:02:40.958 --> 00:02:43.208
He was a beast consumed by lust.

00:02:43.291 --> 00:02:43.833
Arrest him.

00:02:43.833 --> 00:02:44.416
But...

00:02:44.458 --> 00:02:45.208
County magistrate Sun

00:02:45.416 --> 00:02:46.500
Issue a notice.

00:02:46.791 --> 00:02:48.916
Announce that the culprit has been punished.

00:02:52.416 --> 00:02:53.416
