00:03:04.541 --> 00:03:06.541
Sir Li, don't be anxious.

00:03:07.208 --> 00:03:08.166
Think about it.

00:03:08.291 --> 00:03:10.833
We just found the bodies of Liu Gui and Liu Qiaoqiao.

00:03:10.875 --> 00:03:12.625
Now Liu Jiaojiao is missing.

00:03:13.125 --> 00:03:15.375
It's as if we're always one step behind.

00:03:15.958 --> 00:03:18.541
It's like this ghost knows our every move.

00:03:19.958 --> 00:03:22.250
Lin Xiaoran, what do you mean?

00:03:22.958 --> 00:03:24.708
The ghost is among us.

00:03:28.291 --> 00:03:29.750
